snippet.title: [Second Galaxy] Second Galaxy Gameplay Guide ---- Wormholes
snippet.description:
If you're a truly adventurous Commander, wormholes will be your friend in Second Galaxy. We know very little about wormholes, but you can guarantee that you’ll need to be well-prepared in order to explore them.
